Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕拿了嗎 衛生紙拿了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.79,0:00:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以喝生水哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是去叢林探險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行的目的地只是奈良罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到奈良 就是葛根粉條 奈良漬 柿葉壽司 鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 我倒是也沒特別期待著啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別用充滿期待的表情說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.79,0:00:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託請別跟來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘帶東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘帶東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊墜？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個 出行的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:01:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保佑你不會遇到意外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以絕對不可以取下來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愛操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 音姐 昨晚我拜託的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.22,0:01:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心 還有我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好照顧她的 請盡情去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然令人期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛啊 戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離學校 24小時一直待在一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.28,0:03:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種機會不拿來和女孩子相好還能幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不會做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是淡泊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是冷淡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍的大海 青澀的春天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉君還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總比把自己女朋友晾著不管的某人強多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 再這樣說的話機會要溜走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.25,0:04:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓關係比現在更進一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油吧 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會給你打氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完後的便當盒 請分組收集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你拿過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊 空著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了就想睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然也有這個因素
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上音姐她說事前演講什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忽然之間就翻開了歷史教科書…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下面由義之來導遊的話 就可以放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋裡已經什麼都不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概小戀還比較熟悉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是你來給做我導遊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好做導遊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是頭一次兩人出來旅行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起留下兩人的珍貴回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 請問兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊 這不是新婚旅行而是修學旅行的講
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 人家胸卡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 義之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀 看起來很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.83,0:06:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 天枷也很喜歡動物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天枷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她一起來的話一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 接下來去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看舞女姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是在京都嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我推薦的是入鹿的首塚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}蘇我入鹿：日本飛鳥時代的中央豪族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以小看首塚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奈良的非官方指南上可是排首位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女 頭一次在首塚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 再擺開一點 那麼再來4張…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 這深深的歎息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 因為沒和義之君在一起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 小戀還是覺得混浴比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害羞 不要害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.53,0:08:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往的話這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在交往的吧…我和義之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有在期待著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩愛地牽著手漫步在奈良古都 來個充滿愛意的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在耳邊輕述你的美麗勝過那微笑的佛祖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夕陽下的展望台 深情一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但涉和杉並以及我們全都是些電燈泡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人總找不到獨自相處的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.11,0:09:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話當然會留下一聲歎息了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修學旅行大家在一起是理所當然的 也很快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且義之也和平常一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想戀人應該是更加特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗得真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.79,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說 身體已經洗乾淨了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉行那例行的活動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.93,0:10:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去女生房間聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要的就是這個 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女孩子增進友誼的絕佳機會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總不能袖手旁觀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係 男生們一起熱鬧就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.37,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個愛情土豪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你的話會我們會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是打扮好了就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生們的房 間 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見面的話就去見面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說話的話就去說話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躊躇不前是最不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的少女所需要的是行動力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 準備和義之私通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私 私通？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多說無益
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強行帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.31,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.38,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以讓你們去男生房間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.17,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 這也算是救人一命的事情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向得不到回報的戀人伸出愛的援手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學 學校裡禁止不純的異性交往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月島小姐 你的包裹送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義 義之？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙 來女生的房間…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:11:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 與其說是來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不請自來是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來啊 涉那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說誰亂來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是打擊人啊 為你好才把你綁來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 月島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我們就將計就計 我們的房間就給你們兩位慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這不是給我們添亂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 會給其他人添麻煩的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 該吐槽的地方應該不是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 難道說是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我和…義 義之兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 現在才發覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女澡堂中的各位有人丟失手機的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個服務員難道是μ型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是老式旅館 真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅館工作很辛苦的 能派上用場的地方有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的好氣氛給破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 和服挺合身的 也挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 要是我家也有個多好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開玩笑也別拿這事亂開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個不是挺快樂的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鄙視你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻耶 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒怎麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,μ這種機器人 要是沒有就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用把話說到這份上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有 礙著你什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真對你的常識表示懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼這麼討厭μ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟μ有仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不關你什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的聚會搞僵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那麼生氣真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法隆寺充滿著聖德太子一族的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}法隆寺：位於奈良縣生駒郡班鳩町，聖德宗總寺院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說被施了咒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.22,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著像是打不開的門這類七大不可思議現象的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉並君 真是賣力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這算哪門子修學旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長這傢伙 還對昨天的事耿耿於懷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之 我們去看看佛祖大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快來快來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面相好慈祥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛像一直被大家這麼膜拜 敬奉著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣是人造出來的 為什麼μ就不受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想天枷同學的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以擁有自己的心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 義之 你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.01,0:16:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是7萬元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:17:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這可不是隨口開玩笑的吧 由夢這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿角真的打算要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物買什麼決定好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊 你可要好好聽我訴苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要7萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7萬？ 什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角啊 鹿的角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿角？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也知道他少根筋 但沒想到這麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩一天了 你得加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的 拿出點自信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午是最後的自由活動時間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼地方想和義之一起去的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和義之…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算到了 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.31,0:18:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上泡個澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能耽誤些時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.02,0:18:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小戀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 關於明天下午的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是急死人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…明天你有什麼安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.28,0:18:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概隨便轉轉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個超粗神經白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…有個地方想和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日大社
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\pos(352,10)}春日大社：位於奈良市春日野町，舊官幣大社，日本三大神社之一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說那裡供奉著結緣的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結緣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡有心型的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以把兩個人的名字寫在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 就可以和喜歡的人永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管到什麼時候 不管發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人永不分離 戀人們恆久相依
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓戀愛順利的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.78,0:19:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我和義之兩個人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 兩個人一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義之君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 一臉淫笑真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你明天去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為什麼你會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.01,0:20:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們說好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 我的舞女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒抱過 沒抱過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人羨慕死了 你這愛情土豪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不去泡澡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去和音姐通個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗷 羨慕死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小戀 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由夢嗎 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後天就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你那邊怎麼樣
